  "texts": [
    "The objective functions illustrate the adversarial training process, which is critical for GANs, while the gradient descent updates demonstrate the optimization steps taken during training.",
    "Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) play an important role in the success of generative adversarial networks (GANs), particularly in picture production and manipulation.",
    "CNNs' innate capacity to record spatial hierarchies and local patterns aids in the development of realistic pictures by the GAN generator.",
    "Furthermore, CNNs used in the discriminator excel in feature extraction, allowing the network to detect fine characteristics and differentiate between actual and manufactured samples.",
    "This ability to extract features and learn representations enables GANs to tackle a wide range of imagerelated tasks, from style transfer to data augmentation, demonstrating CNNs' adaptability and usefulness in upgrading GAN architectures."
  ],
